</p><p>where
</p>
<ul><li><i>E</i> is the linear light signal normalized by the <a href="/wiki/Reference_white_level" class="mw-redirect" title="Reference white level">reference white level</a> in the range <span class="mwe-math-element"><span class="mwe-math-mathml-inline mwe-math-mathml-a11y" style="display: none;"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"  alttext="{\displaystyle \left[0,12\right]}">
