</math></span><img src="https://wikimedia.org/api/rest_v1/media/math/render/svg/ea67b8f62937a77fca5f7c082bbd4c5cf58b35d0" class="mwe-math-fallback-image-inline" aria-hidden="true" style="vertical-align: -0.671ex; width:12.201ex; height:2.509ex;" alt="{\displaystyle R_{D},G_{D},B_{D}}"></span> in cd/m<sup>2</sup>.</li>
<li><span class="mwe-math-element"><span class="mwe-math-mathml-inline mwe-math-mathml-a11y" style="display: none;"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"  alttext="{\displaystyle E}">
